ore_item_assets/steam/apps/1370170/extras/4a8de4c1b82b7634424d35941ffc3562.webp?t=1765913751\" width=610 height=50 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1370170/extras/136096fa6c9a24b836dbb92aeea459f6.poster.avif?t=1765913751\" width=610 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1370170/extras/136096fa6c9a24b836dbb92aeea459f6.webm?t=1765913751\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1370170/extras/136096fa6c9a24b836dbb92aeea459f6.mp4?t=1765913751\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy seamless gameplay with intuitive camera controls. Easily hide and reveal diorama pieces for a perfect view!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1370170/extras/a050a805365f47e11ebc696c566b37ec.avif?t=1765913751\" width=610 height=150 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >COMPATIBLE WITH THE NEW TILT FIVE™ AUGMENTED REALITY SYSTEM!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Really feel like you are putting together a virtual Diorama, piece by piece as if it were there in front of you.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >For the Tilt Five™ system, modifications designed to improve immersion in the game have been added, including:  </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Navigate the Diorama using the Tilt Five™ wand, with full control of the scenery view, rotating, zooming, and panning; </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > The fourth, which is the game's MENU, was positioned below the Tilt Five™ board, giving the feeling of interacting with a model and choosing options on the objects inside it; </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > After finishing the Dioramas, interact with the Tilt Five™ wand on some objects in the scenery and watch them animate and come to life. </p></li></ul>",
